ion to the safe and effective autonomous navigation for a\nsingle robot working in a dense real human crowd. Our learned policy enables a\nrobot to make effective progress in a crowd without getting stuck. Videos are\navailable at https://sites.google.com/view/hybridmrca\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 11 Aug 2018 17:33:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-14"}
