BB if the\ntemperature is widely distributed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Aug 2018 13:31:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Aug 2018 06:43:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
