\nsignificantly non-zero result, it may be concluded that the physical processes,\nunderlying the variation of the luminosity of PG 1159-035, are non-linear. The\naforementioned result for $\\lambda$ was obtained using the $L^\\infty$-norm\ndistance; a larger, yet not incompatible, result was extracted with the\nEuclidean ($L^2$-norm) distance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 12 Aug 2018 11:11:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Aug 2018 08:18:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-28"}
